{"tid":1777403,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞中場 Arthur 懷疑染上性病","createTime":"2019-12-10T08:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T05:04:08.000Z","uid":31314,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"5b98ff40b212781bf0d5fb8baac982488aa53c35","tid":1777403,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"Arthur Melo: Barcelona midfielder reportedly set to miss upcoming El Clasico due to an alleged encounter with an STD infection.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Barcelona&rsquo;s star midfielder is set to miss Barcelona matches for few weeks after he has reportedly encountered an STD infection</strong></span>, and its treatment will keep him away from matches as its dosages can violate anti-doping norms.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to Andreu Ginola, the reason Arthur Melo did not play against Mallorca was because of a sexually transmitted infection. The club claimed he missed out due to a groin injury, whereas Ginola claims it was due to gonorrhoea.<br />\n<br />\nThis would likely see Arthur sidelined for a few weeks: the medicine for gonorrhoea pops up on anti-doping control&rsquo;s radar, and if tested positive, Arthur would be suspended for months."},{"pid":"3204a44370fcbc3e2eacf8762e288a9f6228b7f1","tid":1777403,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1389f2fdbfa92c591905caffe40e960cc3d64882","tid":1777403,"uid":31314,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"3204a44370fcbc3e2eacf8762e288a9f6228b7f1","tid":1777403,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"感同身受？"},{"pid":"f322c33cc9d7ac4e7141131678c9c510a28e78b2","tid":1777403,"uid":894,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"染上了性病 切割是命途"},{"pid":"4826f6d47f3cd58980df864933453800b3be8829","tid":1777403,"uid":31314,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿今夏斥資4000萬歐元轉會費，由巴甲甘美奧簽下22歲中場艾法美路 (Arthur Melo) ，轉會費金額不低加上旋即穿上傳奇恩尼斯達嘅8號球衣，顯然巴塞對佢期望唔低，都令球迷期待呢位新恩尼斯達嘅表現。事實上，艾法美路於巴塞正式登場之後，有球迷表示認為佢踢法反而有點沙維影子，到底佢係新沙維定新小白？"},{"pid":"b9c60f960105da824467134cc64b5987deced0cd","tid":1777403,"uid":154872,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"比碎右傳染"},{"pid":"ea411c63a447cf465a340b959744d250b9ac9e46","tid":1777403,"uid":371,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"屌過麻友嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5add0bfcc18486ac0ae47065474a3ac708ac364c","tid":1777403,"uid":22589,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"叫g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a14c7126fb9e167d9dbc692bcbe000fafadc50","tid":1777403,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c60f960105da824467134cc64b5987deced0cd","tid":1777403,"uid":154872,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"比碎右傳染"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe0ebb3172bcc3023e69ebc6cf6c04166e5c321","tid":1777403,"uid":15739,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"屌屎窟屌左八十幾年斷咗龜頭返咗雞姦死罪"},{"pid":"5e24b0f79a3899a167706d9b3ff78eab50469f74","tid":1777403,"uid":34293,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"巴閪仔愛屌人妖閪"},{"pid":"742989904bc4aa256b07c14c2a11e47a994a2370","tid":1777403,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ea411c63a447cf465a340b959744d250b9ac9e46","ti